  "prompt": "Where can I get affordable pest control services for bed bugs in Hawkesbury?",
  "response": "To find affordable pest control services for bed bugs in Hawkesbury, you can try the following approaches:\n\n1. **Local Pest Control Companies**: Search for pest control companies in Hawkesbury using Google or local directories. Look for reviews and compare prices.\n\n2. **Online Platforms**: Websites like Airtasker, HomeAdvisor, or Thumbtack allow you to post your job and receive quotes from multiple service providers.\n\n3. **Community Recommendations**: Join local community groups on social media platforms like Facebook or Nextdoor and ask for recommendations for affordable pest control services.\n\n4. **Promotions and Discounts**: Check if any local pest control companies are running promotions or discounts. Some companies offer special rates for first-time customers.\n\n5. **DIY Solutions**: If you're looking to save money, consider researching DIY pest control methods for bed bugs, though this may not be as effective as professional services.\n\n6. **Housing Authorities or Local Health Departments**: Check with local housing authorities or health departments, as they may have resources or recommendations for affordable pest control options.\n\nMake sure to read reviews and verify the credentials of any pest control service you consider to ensure quality and safety.",
